# Authoritative for email-spf-incomplete.demo. — exercises the SPF
# lookup-budget graceful-degradation path (spec 010 US2). The apex SPF
# include:s a sub-name that does NOT exist, so the recursive walk can't
# resolve it: dnshealth_spf_lookup_eval_complete reads 0 (the count is a
# lower bound) and the budget row stays PASS — a transient/unresolvable
# include never produces a false over-budget FAIL.

email-spf-incomplete.demo. {
    file /zones/email-spf-incomplete.demo.zone
    log
    errors
}
